WEBVTT

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:11.720
[kicauan burung]

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:14.680
'Mari kita buat kesepakatan.'

00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:17.320
'Kamu akan melepaskan Adi.'

